    "long_instructions": "## Plan a Trip to Disneyworld\r\n\r\nUse AI Chat to help you plan a trip to Disneyworld. \r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n\r\n1. Start by entering a **generic prompt** and read AI Chat's response. For example: \r\n\r\n>Help me plan a trip to Disneyworld\r\n2. Revise your prompt and add specific examples, like **what rides you want to go on** or **which characters you want to meet**. Press **Send** and read AI Chat's updated response.\r\n2. Finally, re-submit your previous prompt and include an **uploaded image**.\r\n3. Press **Send** and read AI Chat's response.\r\n\r\n**Try it out!**\r\n",
